Q: what is the equivalent of /etc/hosts on XP?
Windows\system32\drivers\etc\hosts
edit the file with notepad!

Q: How to get read of cached password used for mounting shares?
Control Panel > Users > Select user > 
look in left pane, for related tasks
select: Manage my network pasword
More @ how to get ride of cached passwords windows

Q: How to set the CIFS password for a particular user?
Start > Run > control userpasswords2

